			<div class="content">If the 2000 honda were mine I would make sure I had Liability coverage medical coverage and uninsured motorist coverage. What ever happens the car has some value but not much. If you currently have Comp and a bad wndshield get it fixed before dropping the comp and collision coverages.</div>

